Students engage in various activities, such as quietly rehearsing elevator pitches against a wall and participating in an alumni panel discussing interview preparation strategies. Career counselors offer guidance on maintaining eye contact and navigating applicable industries while a live dashboard tracking fair attendance is showcased by a data science company. A small drone from a robotics startup hovers above its booth, drawing attention, as friends decompress on the quad, exchanging their experiences and which companies responded positively.

Event staff scan registrations and distribute lanyards at the entrance, accompanied by a welcome announcement detailing the schedule. Inside, students utilize kiosks and tablets to upload their resumes into the fair database, clutching them in branded folders, while some rehearse their elevator pitches quietly against the wall. Career counselors offer guidance on industry navigation, and an alumni panel discusses preparation for technical interviews. A data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance, and a small drone from a robotics startup captures attention above its booth. Friends decompress on the quad, comparing their experiences and which companies responded warmly, as announcement chimes signal the approaching end, with a post-event survey link displayed near the exit.

Students engage in rehearsing elevator pitches quietly and participate in an alumni panel discussing strategies for preparing for technical interviews, while career counselors offer guidance on networking etiquette and maintaining eye contact. The aroma of coffee and catered snacks fills the air, complemented by a small drone from a robotics startup hovering above its booth. Outside on the quad, friends relax and compare notes on target employers. Monitors display a post-event survey link as students discuss their experiences before exiting.
